text: Victoria Law Courts Birmingham Magistrates' Court is a Magistrates' Court in Birmingham, England. The court sits at Victoria Law Courts on Corporation Street. Proposals to move to a new purpose-built courthouse nearby were suspended in 2010 following the introduction of budgetary restraint imposed by the Government.
